# Prettier 3 also reads .gitignore, so build output (dist/), node_modules/,
# .wrangler/, and scratchpad-* are already excluded there. This file only lists
# tracked files that must stay out of the formatter.

# Generated by drizzle-kit — machine-written SQL + JSON snapshots, never hand-edited
drizzle/

# Bun lockfile — machine-generated
bun.lock

# Markdown is deliberately unformatted (see docs/decisions/prettier-adoption.md):
# Prettier pipe-pads tables so any cell edit re-pads the whole table (giant
# whitespace diffs — the problem this setup exists to prevent) and rewrites
# *italic* as _italic_ across ~46 hand-written docs.
*.md
